Yo, Wilson ., whats your nick in Innoruuk. which city?

For new players in FreePort and on Innoruuk server. u can add me to your "Friend" list. here's how.
type only the words inside the "
type "/Friend Yiyang"
then type " /Who all Friend " this command will list the "Friends" that r currently on-line in the innoruuk

Type "/tell Yiyang" to talk to me. i'll guide u in the limited knowlege i've acquire"
im Level 9 Monk goiin on 10th.

Check out these website : www.eqss.stratics.com , www.missvalley.com/everguide , www.hydracomp.com/Eq/

Cya
